Description: Downloads expected fantasy points data from ffverse repositories if
    available, and otherwise builds up expected points data by applying models to 
    nflverse play-by-play data.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://ffexpectedpoints.ffverse.com,
    https://github.com/ffverse/ffexpectedpoints
